{"tid":1540854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中小企聯合會：林鄭撤回未能解決行業困局","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:56:28.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04440b9badea2d8b30954804144b1f25b072da40","tid":1540854,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"中小企聯合會：林鄭撤回未能解決行業困局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361632&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a9e8fd8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361632&h=b387d100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361632</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】對於政府撤回修例，香港中小型企業聯合會表示，近期的社會事件已經損害了香港國際形象，行政長官林鄭月娥提出撤回修例等措施，已不能解決當前行業所面對的困難。<br />\n<br />\n香港中小型企業聯合會會長麥美儀：「香港正面對兩件事，外憂內患：外是中美貿易戰；內患是這次的破壞，香港依靠的飲食業、旅遊業、酒店業、零售業等都已被破壞，人們已經不來香港。雖然政府有資助，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最可憐是我們想做生意想有人來香港，但他們都不敢再來，整個感覺給人來香港很不安全。</strong></span></span>」"},{"pid":"7c69ffe4ec1740bb3c19ea9c6551144ab2e01011","tid":1540854,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"321e78fc7b891cdeb3afccdce96c88d318663ba6","tid":1540854,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7768e29106e6f456e0e5b31d987d27b8a9fe9cba","tid":1540854,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img s